translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"Ni ichionechela kukwao yakusakala yaŵapanganyisye, ni ichasyungula ayila yaŵaliji nkuitenda chipongwe"
  45,34,"Ni ichiŵechetedwa yanti: “Lelo chitun’diŵalile (m’Moto) mpela yamwatite pakuliŵalila yakusimangana ni lisiku lyenu lyelino, mauto genu ni ku Moto, soni nganinkola jenumanja akunkamuchisya ŵaliose.”"
  45,35,"“Yalakweyo (yaimpatileyo) ni ligongo lyanti jenumanja mwagatendele chipongwe ma Ȃya ga Allah, ni wannyenjile umi wa duniya.” Basi lelo ngakoposyedwa mwalakwemo (m’Moto), soni ŵanganyao ngaakundidwa (kuujila ku duniya) kuti akatende toba ni kuŵenda chikululuko (kwa Allah)"
  45,36,"Basi Allah ni Nsyene lumbili losope lwene, M’mbuje jwa kumawunde, soni M’mbuje jwa petaka, M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"
  45,37,"Soni ukulungwa ni Wakwe kumawunde ni petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  46,1,Hâ. Mîm
  46,2,"Kutulusyidwa kwa Chitabu (Qur’an) kukuumila kwa Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  46,3,"Nganitugumba mawunde ni mataka ni yaili chilikati chakwe ikaŵeje mwakuonaonape ni ndema jekolanjidwe, sano aŵala ŵaakufuulu akuitundumalila yaateteledwe nayo"
  46,4,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ana nkuiona uli ayila yankuiwomba kunneka Allah? Munosyani, ana ni upandechi wetaka waigumbile? Kapena ikwete yalakweyo liunjili lyakamusyangana (najo Allah) ku mawunde? Mumbani chitabu chachapali nkanichiŵe achi (cha Qur’an), kapena sigasiga sya umanyilisyi (syakutendela umboni yagalagatila isanamu), nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  46,5,"Ana ni nduni jwali jwakupotela nnope kumpunda mundu jwaakuiwomba inepe yangaŵaga Allah, ayila yangaŵa nkwajanga mpaka lisiku lya Kiyama, soni yalakwe ngaikumanyilila ya maduwa gao (kuti akuiwomba)"